title: [Ta'Illistim, Caear Var]
description: Profusely blooming cascades of miniature roses trail from the windowboxes of a nearby shop.  A small basket of flowers rests on the doorstep, and an engraved silver sign is mounted upon the cottage's pale blue painted door.
